Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on the phone with\Nyour girlfriend ,she's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,隔窗看到你打着电话和你女友争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going off about\Nsomething that you said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她任性的拒绝了你所说的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause she doesn't, get\Nyour humor like I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她并不像我幽默善解人意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这个房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a typical Tuesday night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个普通的周二晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to the kind\Nof music she doesn't like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,房间里充斥着和她截然相反的曲风
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and she'll never know\Nyour story like I do ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,窃喜她并不像我一样了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wears short skirts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可她穿短裙如此妖娆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wear T-shirts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只穿宽松T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cheer captain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她是啦啦队最璀璨的头牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm on the bleachers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只能在偷偷混进场内远眺你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming about the\Nday when you wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我多希望有一天你醒来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.97,0:00:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And find that what you're looking\Nfor has been here the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,发现你所寻找的那个东西已经在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could see that I'm\Nthe one who understands you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能有幸看到我才是那个懂你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,been here all along\Nso why can't you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:01:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你看不见我一直在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.51,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你也只能属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk in the streets with\Nyou in your worn-out jeans
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿着破洞牛仔裤闲庭信步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help thinking\Nthis is how it ought to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在公园的长凳上你为我撩发时我知道你不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughing on a park\Nbench, thinking to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但我特别希望我的内心能够做点让你愉悦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey isn't this easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿这真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got a smile that\Ncould light up this whole town
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的微笑照亮了我心中的整个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen it in a while\Nsince she brought you down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,自从她使你失落后我就再没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you're fine
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你一切安好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you better than that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可我比她更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey what you doing\Nwith a girl like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿你难道对这样的女孩子不心动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She wears high heels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她穿着高跟鞋韵味十足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wear sneakers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿着运动鞋土的掉渣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s cheer captain and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她是啦啦队最璀璨的头牌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the bleachers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可我只能乔装打扮混入场内偷偷远眺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreaming about the day\Nwhen you wake up and find
