Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I remember you driving to my\Nhouse in the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得你开车参加舞会的夜晚我带上了那张纸条
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who makes you laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当你被挫折磨砺非常难过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When you know\Nyou're about to cry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是那个能让你开怀大笑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know your favorite songs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你最喜欢的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you tell me\Nabout your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你也和我敞开心扉聊了你的星辰大海
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know where you belong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你以后身处何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know it's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that I'm\Nthe one who understands you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法看到我才是那个懂你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Been here all along
